videos.description: Michigan State's Cassius Winston collects the steal, drives and flips it to Joshua Langford for the open three.
videos.headline: Michigan State turns D into 3

videos.description: Michigan State's Kyle Ahrens tips the ball to himself to save a turnover and then finishes at the rim.
videos.headline: Ahrens tips it to himself, then lays it in

videos.description: Michigan State's quick passing leads to a Matt McQuaid open three to put the Spartans up 31-15.
videos.headline: Michigan State's great ball movement leads to 3

videos.description: Michigan State's Nick Ward slams it home with nasty one-handed dunk off an Xavier Tillman assist.
videos.headline: Ward throws it down on one-handed dunk

videos.description: Michigan State's Cassius Winston races down the court, hesitates and floats it up to Nick Ward who flies to lay it in plus the foul.
videos.headline: Ward gets air and lays it in plus the foul

videos.description: Michigan State gets the offensive rebound after a Matt McQuaid missed 3-pointer that results in a Kyle Ahrens dunk.
videos.headline: Ahrens hammers two-handed dunk

videos.description: Michigan State's Nick Ward denies Florida Gulf Coast's Brady Ernst as he goes for the dunk.
videos.headline: Ward clears Enst's dunk attempt
